Welcome to eConstat TN, an app that helps you easily and quickly fill in reports. In order to use the app, you will need to create an account. By creating an account and using the app, you agree to be bound by these terms and conditions.

Data CollectioneConstat TN collects personal information from you in order to provide you with the best possible experience. This includes information such as your name, email address, address, information about your car, and information about your car s insurance in order to make the process easier, as well as any other information you choose to provide.eConstat TN does not display any advertising to you.
Device AccesseConstat\n TN requires access to your device s camera in order to function properly. By using the app, you grant eConstat TN permission to access your device s camera.

Third-Party Integrations\neConstat TN uses a Node.js server to store and process data. By using the app, you agree to the collection, use, and sharing of your data as described in these terms and conditions.

Changes to These Terms\neConstat TN reserves the right to update these terms and conditions at any time. If we make any changes, we will post the revised terms and conditions on this page and will indicate the effective date of the revised terms and conditions. We encourage you to review these terms and conditions periodically to stay informed about our practices.
Contact UsIf you have any questions about these terms and conditions, please contact us at rayen.harhouri@esprit.tn

This icon represents the location of any damage to your car . If the icon is displayed , it indicates that your car has been damaged in that particular location . For example , if the icon is located at the top left of the screen , it means that your car has been damaged in the top left area.

This icon represents the location of any protected parts of your car.If the shield icon is displayed, it indicates that your car does not have any damage in that particular location.For example,if the shield icon is located at the top left,means that that area of your car does not have any damage.
